{
  "texts": [
    "Research [85] release a dataset for claim verification, which are derived from subset of news title from Arabic News Text (ANT) corpus [94].",
    "The authors modified news title to generate fake claims.",
    "For classification process, they used BERT, and LSTM for training and testing datasets.",
    "The study reported that BERT provides best F1-score registered which are 64.3%.",
    "Compared to this research, Nagoudi [84] used the same dataset from [85] in addition to their dataset which is automatically generated fake news from real one."
  ]
}